title: March’s French Vogue Features Its First Transgender Cover Model
text: A fashion magazine’s March issue is the second biggest of the year, after the unbelievably hefty September one. And French Vogue just made their March issue an even bigger deal by putting a transgender model on the cover for the first time. Brazilian model Valentina Sampaio appears in a metallic... More »
